{"tid":2300783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国国安威武，异地冻结本人房产","createTime":"2020-11-25T20:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T20:56:22.000Z","uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6732e7081d0850026d85bd0537808b42938be822","tid":2300783,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T20:54:12.000Z","msg":"我在中国成都全款购买了一套期房，当地房管部门拒绝办理房产证，官式答复说委托书笔迹不对，需要我亲自前去更正。然而，工作人员私下承认：这套房子是被我老家的国安局异地查封（准确的说，是冻结）的。可见所谓笔迹问题是诱饵，中国政府在请我入瓮。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美国之音详细报道</strong>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/5670863.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2F5670863.html&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=abfbdc1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/5670863.html</a><br />\n<strong>回忆雨伞革命的个人旧作</strong>：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go6LY0m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo6LY0m.png&h=224c2e6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1d9aca1fd15dd5912bb96427037a4d6e7b2c2ce","tid":2300783,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T20:56:22.000Z","msg":"反抗吧"}]}